description:
Welcome to the Online Entrepreneurship course. In this short free course i will explain to you some popular terms in Online business. Also you will learn about some basic tools you will need to start and maintain successful online business.

You will learn about :

- link tracking

- solo ads

- attraction marketing

- ppc and ppv ads

- sales funnel

and many more things.

This course is planed as introduction to online entrepreneusrhip and it is created for complete beginners.

Thank you for shoving your interest.

Feel free to check out my other courses!
title: Entrepreneur from Bedroom - The basics of online marketing
